Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.47,0:03:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託妳, 速瀨中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.97,0:03:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,至少進行支援砲擊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.39,0:03:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
